flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Customer or dealer initiates an order change or cancellation request.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Receive order change/cancellation request]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Remote Functions - Validate request against policies]
  N2 --> N3[Stream: STREAMS - Assess impact on production and delivery]
  N3 --> N4{PB: CWB Lifecycle - Determine decision (accept}
  N4 -->|Primary| N5[PB: Notification - Communicate decision to customer]
  N5 --> N6[PB: Remote Functions - Update order status and issue refund if applicable]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced COGS impact, preserved OTIF, improved cash flow through timely refunds and accurate order fulfillment.]
  N4 -->|Request exceeds policy limits| B1[Escalate to supervisor]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Manual review and decision]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N4 -->|Impact assessment indicates significa...| B2[Modify request or escalate]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Adjusted request or manual intervention]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N4 -->|Customer requests expedited refund| B3[Expedite refund process]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Faster refund issuance]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]